<h1>THE FIRST ONES — A Complete Worldbuilding Bible</h1>

<blockquote>*Vhor'ketha eth-shaen, vhor'ketha eth-vael.*  <br>
*To pour through is to be remembered; to be remembered is to remain.*  <br>
— fragment, attributed to the late Vhor'kethi era, speaker unknown</blockquote>

<hr>

<h2 id="table-of-contents">TABLE OF CONTENTS</h2>

<p>1. <a href="#i-the-first-ones--origin-and-nature">The First Ones — Origin and Nature</a></p>
<p>2. <a href="#ii-the-arrival-of-humans-and-the-great-fading">The Arrival of Humans and the Great Fading</a></p>
<p>3. <a href="#iii-the-bond--vhor'keth-and-vhor'ketha">The Bond — Vhor'keth and Vhor'ketha</a></p>
<p>4. <a href="#iv-the-fall--the-betrayal-and-the-chains">The Fall — The Betrayal and the Chains</a></p>
<p>5. <a href="#v-the-origin-of-wizards--genetics">The Origin of Wizards — Genetics</a></p>
<p>6. <a href="#vi-the-present-state-of-the-first-ones">The Present State of the First Ones</a></p>
<p>7. <a href="#vii-the-old-tongue">The Old Tongue</a></p>
